{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_52_03",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 3話 ファイト、十七歳……！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "登山と聞いて険しい山道を覚悟してましたけど\nこの山は道が整備されていて歩きやすいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I heard we’d be hiking‚ I was prepared for a rough mountain trail‚\nbut this mountain has well-maintained paths‚ so it’s easy to walk.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "頂上まで行くのは大変ですが\n山登りに不慣れな俺でもこれならなんとか登れそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Getting to the summit is still tough‚\nbut even someone like me who’s not used to hiking can manage this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.1758728027
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "ぜぇ、ぜぇ……はぁ、はぁ……ふぅ、ふぅ……\nまだ行けるわ、遙子……！　ファイト、十七歳……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huff‚ huff… hah‚ hah… wheeze‚ wheeze…\nI can keep going‚ Haruko…! Come on‚ seventeen…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……は、遙子さん？　大丈夫ですか？\nやっぱり荷物、持ちましょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…H-Haruko-san? Are you okay?\nShould I carry your luggage after all?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.6566431682
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "だ、大丈夫よ、これくらい。キャンプの時はいつも\n一人で荷物を運んでるんだから……はぁ、はぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I’m fine‚ this is nothing. When I go camping‚\nI always carry my gear by myself… hah‚ hah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.2758042336
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……ねぇ？\nそろそろ休憩の時間じゃないかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whew… hey?\nDon’t you think it’s about time for a break?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "まだ登り始めたばかりですよ。バテバテじゃないですか\n遙子さんの分も俺が持つので、荷物を渡して下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ve only just started climbing—you’re already worn out‚ aren’t you?\nI’ll carry yours too‚ so please hand it over.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.897209565
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、{user}君には沢山荷物を\n持ってもらってるのに、これ以上持たせるのは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you’re already carrying so much‚ {user}-kun‚\nit wouldn’t be right to make you carry even more…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.6872527164,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.9620170754
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "あ……私の荷物をそんなに軽々と……案外力持ちなのね\n普段はそんな風に見えないから、ちょっと意外だわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… you’re lifting my bag so easily… you’re stronger than I thought.\nYou don’t usually look that strong‚ so it’s a bit surprising.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.3666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 66.9620170754
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（くっ……重いけど、遙子さんに無理をさせる訳には）\n（いかないし、ここは俺が頑張らないと！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ghh… it’s heavy‚ but I can’t let Haruko-san push herself…）\n（This is where I have to step up!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.9522428992
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとう。{user}君は\nやっぱり優しいわね。かっこいいわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Thank you. You really are\nkind‚ {user}-kun. You’re very cool.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.3333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_mountain-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6605.712527099996,
          "startTime": 98.9390458604
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "―― 一時間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "— One hour later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.4923791728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.8390458586
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.8390458586
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……よいしょ、と……！\nやっと頂上に着いた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa‚ haa… heave-ho…!\nWe finally made it to the summit…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.1666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 99.3
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3360.953632800005,
          "startTime": 103.0666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "よく頑張ったわね、お疲れ様\nほら見て、頂上からの眺めは最高よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You did great—good work.\nLook‚ the view from the top is amazing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.3421567283
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "今日は晴れてるから富士山がよく見えるわ\n向こうは南アルプスの山々ね。雄大でとっても綺麗……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s clear today‚ so you can see Mount Fuji really well.\nOver there are the Southern Alps—so grand and beautiful…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.725434383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "この眺めは感動しますね……。遙子さんとこの景色を\n見られただけでも、頑張った甲斐がありました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This view is breathtaking… Just being able to see it\nwith you made all the effort worth it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.6915672305
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "まだまだ、お楽しみはこれからよ。大自然を眺めながら\n美味しい山ご飯を二人でいただきましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The best part is still ahead. While admiring the great outdoors‚\nlet’s enjoy some delicious mountain food together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_mountain-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4302.293141999997,
          "startTime": 146.3689598087
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.1022924426
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "いただきまーす！　……うーん、美味しい～！\n綺麗な景色を眺めながら食べるお肉は最高ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s eat! …Mmm‚ it’s delicious!\nMeat tastes best when you eat it while enjoying a beautiful view.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "ほらほら、遠慮しないでどんどん食べて\n野菜も美味しいわよ。マシュマロも焼こうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ don’t hold back—eat up.\nThe vegetables are great too. Shall we grill some marshmallows?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 167.6987345699
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん、なんだかはしゃいでますね\nもしかしてもう飲んでるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem really excited‚ Haruko-san.\nHave you already started drinking?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 174.1120905243
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ……買っておいた山梨ワイン開けちゃった\n{user}君も飲むでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufufu… I opened the Yamanashi wine we bought.\nYou’ll drink too‚ right‚ {user}-kun?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 181.3258146924
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "こうやって二人でお酒を飲むのも久しぶりね\n近頃は忙しくて、ゆっくり話す機会もなかったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s been a while since we drank together like this.\nWe’ve been so busy lately‚ we haven’t had time to talk properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "星見市にいた頃は遙子さんと毎日一緒だったのに\n今はそれも懐かしいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Back when we were in Hoshimi City‚ we were together every day.\nThat feels so nostalgic now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 197.0157692593
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "ほんとよ。最近は全然構ってくれなくて……\nもっと私に構ってくれないと拗ねちゃうんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It really does. You barely spend time with me these days…\nIf you don’t give me more attention‚ I’ll sulk‚ you know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……遙子さん、もう酔ってます？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Haruko-san‚ are you already drunk?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.5873776755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 209.714021667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "そうかもね。山の上だと酔いが回りやすいって言うし\nこんなに楽しく感じるのは、酔っちゃったからかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe. They say alcohol hits harder up in the mountains.\nMaybe it feels this fun because I’m a little tipsy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 216.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "……君、この間まで高校生だったのに、いつの間にか\n大人になって……たくましくて、頼もしくなったよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You were a high school student not that long ago‚ but before I knew it‚\nyou became an adult—strong and reliable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 224.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 230.3128424488
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんだって、人気者になって、みんなが遙子さんを\n褒めて……自信が付いて、もっと可愛くなりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You too‚ Haruko-san—you’ve become so popular‚ everyone praises you‚\nyou’ve gained confidence and become even cuter.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 234.9479047659,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 239.7254951639
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "か、可愛いって……\nもう、そういうとこだぞー？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "C-Cute…?\nCome on‚ that’s what I mean about you~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 242.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 246.0320032917
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "……ふふ、本当に楽しいわね\n今日は君を誘って良かったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Fufu‚ this really is fun.\nI’m glad I invited you today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 250.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 253.082320468
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……お酒が回ってきたみたい\n安心したら、なんだか眠くなってきちゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… the alcohol’s really kicking in.\nNow that I feel relaxed‚ I’m getting sleepy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 257.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 261.1624561949
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-hrk020.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと肩、借りるね……\n……すぅ、すぅ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll borrow your shoulder for a bit…\n…Zzz‚ zzz…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 264.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "え、俺の肩に頭を乗せて……こんな姿勢でちゃんと\n寝られるのか？　寝顔は心地よさそうだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh‚ she put her head on my shoulder… can she really\nsleep properly like this? She looks comfortable‚ though…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 273.262606496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-noon",
      "startTime": 278.2239521983
    },
    {
