      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "……まぁ、いいか。遙子さん、いつもお疲れ様です\n俺が見てますから、今日はゆっくり休んで下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Well‚ I guess it’s fine. You work hard every day‚ Haruko-san.\nI’ll keep watch‚ so please rest well today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 284.8,
      "sfxList": []
